# --- Stellar data grids (downloaded, never committed) ---
# MIST .track.eep / isochrone files and any other large grids live under data/
# but must be fetched at build time, not stored in git (see STAR_SIM_SPEC.md §6).
/data/*
!/data/.gitkeep
!/data/README.md

